```

### Conclusion

Debugging deadlocks in a oneTBB application requires a systematic approach to analyzing thread behavior and synchronization patterns. By implementing the strategies mentioned above, you can effectively identify and resolve deadlocks in your applications. Additionally, continuous monitoring and code refactoring can reduce the likelihood of these issues occurring in the future.

